text: Kathryn Chandria Manuel Bernardo (born March 26, 1996) is a Filipina actor who became known for playing Mara in the TV show Mara Clara (2010–2011). She has also starred in other TV shows Princess and I (2012–2013), Got to Believe (2013–2014), Pangako Sa 'Yo (2015–2016), and La Luna Sangre (2017–2018). She has also starred in different films such as Way Back Home (2011), Must Be... Love (2013), She's Dating the Gangster (2014), Crazy Beautiful You (2015), Barcelona: A Love Untold (2016), Can't Help Falling in Love (2017), The Hows of Us (2018), Three Words to Forever (2018), and Hello, Love, Goodbye (2019). == References == Category:1996 births Category:Filipino actors Category:People from Central Luzon
